						<summary>

						<p>On a stone set up in Ayyanakoḷḷa near the Īśvara temple on the Gajēndragaḍ hill.</p>						

						<p>Circa 17th century.</p>						

						<p>The date of the record is lost. It records a gift to Chenabasapa by <hi rend="italic">Dēsāyi</hi> Surapa-Liṅgapa.</p>						

